headline: Texas Pacific Land Corporation Sets Dates for Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: DALLAS, October 09, 2025--Texas Pacific Land Corporation (NYSE: TPL) (the "Company") announced today that the Company will release third quarter 2025 financial results after the market closes on Wednesday, November 5, 2025. A conference call will be held on Thursday, November 6, 2025 at 10:30 a.m. Eastern Time.
